Package: lpirfs
Type: Package
Title: Estimate Impulse Response Functions based on Local Projections by Jordà (2005)
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Philipp Adämmer
Maintainer: Philipp Adämmer <adaemmer@hsu-hh.de>
BugReports: https://github.com/AdaemmerP/lpirfs/issues
Description: The package contains functions to estimate linear and non-linear impulse 
             responses based on the local projection method by Jordà (2005) <doi:10.1257/0002828053828518>
             Non-linear impulse responses are estimated for two regimes which are estimated with 
             a transition function, proposed by Auerbach and Gorodnichenko (2012) <doi:10.1257/pol.4.2.1>.
License: GPL (>= 2)
Encoding: UTF-8
